### Get Auth Token
# @name login
POST {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/auth/email/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{TEST_EMAIL}}",
  "password": "{{TEST_PASSWORD}}"
}

### Set token variable from login response
@token = {{login.token}}

### ===========================================
### DELETE DIVISIONS ENDPOINTS
### ===========================================

### Delete Division by ID
DELETE {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/divisions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### BULK DELETE DIVISIONS ENDPOINTS
### ===========================================

### Bulk Delete Divisions (Small Batch)
DELETE {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/divisions/bulk-delete
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "ids": [10, 11, 12]
}
